flowchart TB
    Call([Evaluate candidate])
    Call --> Try1[Subprocess backend<br/>real venv, real LLM calls,<br/>real tools, real network]
    Try1 -- ok --> Score1[score &amp; spans<br/>SourceTag = Real]
    Try1 -- recoverable failure --> Try2[Shadow backend<br/>real subprocess, real LLM,<br/>cassette-replayed HTTP/tools/browser]
    Try2 -- ok --> Score2[score &amp; spans<br/>SourceTag = ShadowReplay]
    Try2 -- non-recoverable --> Try3[Static backend<br/>no execution; reason from<br/>code + cached traces only]
    Try3 --> Score3[score &amp; spans<br/>SourceTag = StaticOnly]
    Score1 --> Conf{Confidence aggregation<br/>0.0–1.0}
    Score2 --> Conf
    Score3 --> Conf
    Conf -- high --> Auto[auto-accept eligible]
    Conf -- medium --> Flag[flag for review]
    Conf -- low --> Reject[reject signal]
    classDef good fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#10b981
    classDef warn fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b
    classDef bad fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444
    class Try1,Score1 good
    class Try2,Score2 warn
    class Try3,Score3 bad
